<quantity box="[313,410,1601,1627]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="214" unit="mm" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3–4 mm</quantity>
, all four leaflets more or less equal, the interfoliar segments 
<quantity box="[1103,1228,1601,1627]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" metricValueMax="1.4" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="13" pageNumber="214" unit="mm" value="12.0" valueMax="14.0" valueMin="10.0">10–14 mm</quantity>
